1. There are four files source files included in this folder:

	

	cacheLinearRead.c

	cacheLinearWrite.c

	cacheRandomRead.c

	cacheRandomWrite.c



2. Do 'make all' in the folder to generate the object files for all of these source files.


3. To change the arraysize for the files, edit the arr_size macro in the indiviual files. Comments have been added in the files appropriately.


4. On running the object files the access time per reference is printed out in the end.


5. Change the array size  and repeat the process to observe the memory mountain plot.
